Home

As one of South Wales largest independent plant glazing companies, Lees Plant & Commercial Windscreens have been trading for over 25 years providing many of the regions leading plant hire companies with a replacement glazing service.

We carry large stocks of curved and tempered glass for all makes including Caterpillar, JCB, Komatsu, Takeuchi, Yanmar etc.

We offer a fully mobile service throughout South Wales and the UK through our Nationwide onsite membership. All of our mobile workshops are fully equipped with the latest electric cut-out tools and equipment to minimise your vehicle down time.

Our glaziers are fully trained and have extensive knowledge of all aspects of contractors plant glazing. All our glaziers hold SPA safety passports.
